&lt;li&gt;Orchestrate core executive and leadership meetings, including weekly operating reviews, bi-weekly strategy sessions, and company-wide forums&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare agendas, materials, and pre-reads; capture decisions and action items; and ensure consistent follow-through&lt;/li&gt;
