&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to thrive in a dynamic and exhilarating environment where you&#39;ll be entrusted with significant responsibilities? Are you seeking to join an extraordinary team of young, motivated, and highly ambitious individuals? If you have a genuine passion for connecting with people and driving remarkable outcomes, then you could be the perfect fit for our Chief of Staff&amp;nbsp;position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are on a mission to help consumers save time and money by matching them with the best products for their needs with banking, insurance and utilities. Samlino Group (&lt;a href=&quot;https://samlinogroup.com/&quot;&gt;https://samlinogroup.com/&lt;/a&gt;) operates across three markets, we empowered over 10 million users last year alone, propelling them toward living healthier financial lives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our Chief of Staff, you get the unique opportunity to be a key driver of our exponential growth curve. Sunny Lisbon will be your home base, but you’ll travel to and work with our three markets! To facilitate a steep growth curve, we provide you with the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The chance to create a genuine impact - experience the thrill of working in a fast-paced environment where your efforts and results are tangible, shaping the destiny of our business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspiration and guidance - work closely with our high-performing teams alongside our international peers and founder.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlimited growth potential in our company - we firmly believe in nurturing talent from within, fostering an environment where the sky&#39;s the limit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The passport to adventure - as a part of our international organization, you spread your wings and learn from our other markets while applying both strategic and executive skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invaluable transferable skills - fuel your interpersonal, digital, entrepreneurial, organizational, project management, and business prowess through hands-on experience in an organisation that values training and development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own your own projects and be responsible for driving results across various projects and initiatives. Responsibilities in this job will evolve and be defined and redefined throughout your time with us. The aim is to take ownership of and drive the development of progressively larger opportunities. Success requires the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setting ambitious yet achievable goals, developing strategic plans to reach them, and executing with urgency and intensity to deliver measurable outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of assigned projects or tasks from inception to completion, including defining clear objectives, plans, and deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify potential bottlenecks or obstacles and develop mitigation strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability by ensuring all team members understand their roles and responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a champion for our results-driven culture within the team and organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, coach, and empower A+ teams to reach their potential and provide 5-star experiences to our users and partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project-based assignments with clear objectives spread across different geographies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep dive into value creation, process improvement and organizational growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thinking out of the box, brainstorming and strategizing to challenge status quo and aim at accelerating our momentum and efficient scaling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we expect from you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic individual who thrives in a results-oriented environment to join our team and help us reach our objectives. Industry experience is not a requirement, but you do need to be highly ambitious, proactive, forward-thinking, a fast learner, and driven to succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Furthermore, we are looking for candidates who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have proactive mindset, strong analytical skills, and the ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are self-motivated, detail-oriented, and possess a track record of successfully owning projects from conception to completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess an unwavering drive and desire to be the very best at what they do&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are passionate about making an impact and driving tangible results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exude an unparalleled work ethic fueled by an urgency to progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embrace ownership and proactively following through on commitments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess an insatiable curiosity about business, data, and people, relishing the opportunity to build and nurture relationships that fuel lasting success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master the art of communication, wielding their words with impact both verbally and in writing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Showcase unrivalled organizational skills, skillfully structuring and prioritizing their work to achieve maximum efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Native Danish speaker, fluent in English and an EU work permit is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start Date and Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible start date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will be full time, onsite in Lisbon, Portugal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It will cover all three markets, so regular travel will be part of what we have in mind for you! It will also include extended stays working hands-on with the teams in the different locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(236, 240, 241);&quot;&gt;#LI-Onsite&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;CLEAR is building THE secure identity company of the future. Our mission is to make experiences safer and easier—physically and digitally. With more than 38 million Members and a growing network of partners across the world, CLEAR&#39;s secure identity platform is transforming the way people live, work, and travel. Whether it’s at the airport, stadium, or throughout your everyday life, CLEAR unlocks the magic of frictionless experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Chief of Staff to the President is a critical role operating at the strategic center of a high-growth public company during a period of transformational change. You will help inform the strategy and decisions that define CLEARs role in a rapidly evolving landscape with a direct line of sight into strategy, commercial, operations, partnerships, acquisitions, and board governance. This role provides a springboard for a high-potential professional for executive leadership and we are committed to your development and transition into a senior role within CLEAR.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Serve as a trusted advisor to the President, pressure-testing assumptions, shaping decision framing, and ensuring critical enterprise decisions are informed by the right data and stakeholder input&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop strategic analyses and business cases across CLEAR’s highest-priority initiatives, including new vertical expansion, competitive positioning, partnerships, and AI-driven identity infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Design and manage the President’s operating cadence, ensuring leadership meetings, governance forums, and business reviews drive clarity, alignment, and accountability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Lead cross-functional strategic initiatives end-to-end, particularly those that require senior-level coordination and execution discipline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Represent and support the President in engagements with internal and external stakeholders, including Board preparation, investor materials, executive communications, and key partnership interactions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you&#39;ll measure success:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The President’s top strategic priorities quickly advance with clear ownership, measurable outcomes, and cross-functional alignment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Enterprise-level decisions are made with increased speed and quality, grounded in strong data, framing, and stakeholder coordination&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The operating cadence of the President’s leadership forums runs with discipline, clarity, and minimal organizational friction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Measurable progress in your executive readiness, including expanded scope, strategic judgment, and influence across senior leadership&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;re great at:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Prior experience as a Chief of Staff or in a high-impact operating role within high-growth, scaled organizations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Structuring complex strategic problems and translating analysis into clear, actionable recommendations for senior executives and Boards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Drafting Board-ready memos and executive presentations with precision, clarity, and strong executive presence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Building scalable operating rhythms, project plans, and accountability systems that convert strategy into execution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Influencing senior stakeholders with sound judgment, discretion, urgency, and low-ego collaboration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll be Rewarded:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;At CLEAR, we help YOU move forward - because when you’re at your best, we’re at our best. You’ll work with talented team members motivated by our mission of making experiences safer and easier. Our offices are bright and energetic with an open concept and plenty of conference rooms and casual co-working spaces. We also offer catered lunches every day and have fully stocked kitchens. Outside of the office, we invest in your well-being and learning &amp;amp; development with stipends and reimbursement programs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We offer holistic total rewards, including comprehensive healthcare plans, family-building benefits (fertility and adoption/surrogacy support), flexible time off, annual wellness stipend, free OneMedical memberships for you and your dependents, a CLEAR Plus membership, and a 401(k) retirement plan with employer match. &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The base salary range for this role is $200,000-$250,000, depending on levels of skills and experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The base salary range represents the low and high end of CLEAR’s salary range for this position. Salaries will vary depending on various factors which include, but are not limited to location, education, skills, experience and performance. The range listed is just one component of CLEAR’s total compensation package for employees and other rewards may include annual bonuses, commission, Restricted Stock Units&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;CLEAR provides reasonable accommodation to qualified individuals with disabilities or protected needs. Please let us know if you require a reasonable accommodation to apply for a job or perform your job. Examples of reasonable accommodation include, but are not limited to, time off, extra breaks, making a change to the application process or work procedures, policy exceptions, providing documents in an alternative format, live captioning or using a sign language interpreter, or using specialized equipment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are committed to a transparent and secure hiring process. All communications related to this role will come directly from a CLEAR employee through valid CLEAR channels (e.g., a valid @clearme.com email address or verified CLEAR LinkedIn profile). We encourage candidates to remain alert to job scams and to report any suspicious activity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;#LI-Onsite&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to build something truly extraordinary? Are you driven by the challenge of scaling across markets, building and leading high-performing teams, and shaping the future of venture investing? If you have a fire in your belly, the ability to inspire others, and the desire to spend your days building and leading – this one’s for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an exceptional Chief of Staff to lead CVX Ventures through its next phase of expansion, both in existing and new markets. You’ll be the driving force behind our mission to build Europe’s largest and most active angel investor network - a place where capital meets competence to create extraordinary companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Chief of Staff you’ll be at the forefront of everything CVX is and will become. This is a hands-on leadership role where you’ll shape vision, execute strategy, and hire and inspire teams across borders. You’ll set the standard and pace for how we operate and grow, while being ready to relocate temporarily as new markets open.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We connect experienced professionals and investors with carefully selected, high-potential startups and growth companies. As a member of our network, you&#39;re not just investing capital—you&#39;re bringing your knowledge, experience, and network into play to actively create value and drive growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CVX Ventures is one of Europe&#39;s fastest growing venture investors. We empower our partners to invest in hand-picked cases that match their interests, industries, and expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since 2020 our community has grown to include over 700 members—from angel investors and board members to C-level leaders—who have collectively invested more than EUR 100 million into 100+ companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Being part of CVX means becoming part of a trusted network where deals are sourced with care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CVX currently consists of 20 ambitious and talented individuals with an expectation to be +100 in the next 24 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As our Chief of Staff you will:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the growth and execution across all CVX markets, existing and new ones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, manage and inspire high-performing local teams in each market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the global strategy, from market entry to operational excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the continuous expansion of our angel investor network across Europe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent CVX publicly - at events, conferences, and in media - building visibility and trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be involved in deal flow, investment decisions, and startup ecosystem engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive culture, excellence, and performance across all markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report directly to the Board.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We ideally see that you are:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-7 years of top tier management consulting or investment banking, combined with some start up or venture/private equity investment experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to relocate to new markets for a few months when opening new offices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Great with people – you connect fast and lead with trust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unusually driven and ambitious – you want to win at everything you do and bring others with you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly analytical with strong problem-solving abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strategic thinker who doesn’t mind getting your hands dirty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A front-row seat to building one of Europe’s most exciting venture platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full ownership and responsibility from day one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A company with real traction and an ambitious vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The chance to build your own legacy alongside other top-tier talent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A mix of competitive base salary + significant equity upside.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start Date:&lt;/strong&gt; As soon as possible&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Europe or the UK.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Trives du i et dynamisk og tempofyldt miljø, hvor du får et stort strategisk og operationelt ansvar? Vil du være en del af et exceptionelt entreprenant team med unge, motiverede og ekstremt ambitiøse mennesker? Og er du nysgerrig eller passioneret omkring venturekapital? Hvis ja, så kunne du være vores nye Chief of Staff&amp;nbsp; i Danmark.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Din Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vi søger en dynamisk og strategisk Chief of Staff til at lede vores danske afdeling i København mod fortsat vækst og succes. Du vil være ansvarlig for at forme virksomhedens vision, drive operationel ekspertise og sikre langsigtet rentabilitet. Den ideelle kandidat er en stærk leder med en naturlig evne til at opbygge tillid og relationer. Du er desuden ekstremt drevet, hands-on og har evnen til at inspirere et højtydende team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vores Mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CVX er en af Europas hurtigst voksende ventureinvestorer og er i færd med at blive Europas største ventureinvestor ved at give vækstvirksomheder kapital, viden og netværk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vi er drevet af troen på, at de bedste investorer ofte er dem, der kan give iværksættere den rette viden, erfaring og netværk til deres specifikke stadie og branche.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CVX investerer altid med og gennem de bedste business angels for den enkelte iværksætter. I dag har vi over 600 business angel-partnere i CVX, som investerer i og støtter virksomheder, hvor de kan gøre en forskel med kapital, kompetencer og netværk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CVX består i øjeblikket af 20 ambitiøse og talentfulde individer i København, London &amp;amp; Oslo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dine Ansvarsområder&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Definere og eksekvere din strategi og løbende tilpasse den&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lede den danske ekspansion, herunder potentielle opkøb&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have ansvar for den danske P&amp;amp;L og overordnede drift&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Udbyg og fasthold en stor og værdiskabende pulje af partnere&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Udvikle og lede et topklasse-team på 15 personer inden for salg, bestyrelseshåndtering, events &amp;amp; medlemmer, samt marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identificere og tiltrække de bedste investeringscases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lede investeringsaftaler fra start til slut – fra deal sourcing til investering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repræsentere CVX ved events, samlinger, konferencer osv.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dine Kvalifikationer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Høj arbejdsmoral med en stærk ”sense of urgency”&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Usædvanlig stærk drivkraft og lyst til at være den bedste inden for dit felt&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ års erfaring, ideelt set fra management consulting, investment banking, venturekapital, højvækst-startups eller lignende dynamiske miljøer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proaktiv tilgang og evne til at tage ejerskab over alt, hvad du gør&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dybt engagement i venturekapital- og startup-miljøet med passion for analyse og investering i virksomheder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evne til at samle mennesker og skabe stærke relationer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dygtig til at kommunikere effektivt på management- og bestyrelsesniveau&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evne til at vinde tillid hos forretningsledere&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fremragende analytiske og strukturerede problemløsningsevner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dokumenteret succes i at opnå og overgå indtægtsmål&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Naturlig salgsevne og evne til at arbejde strategisk og operationelt med salg&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stærke lederevner, gerne med tidligere erfaring i ledelse af teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flydende på dansk og engelsk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gerne et eksisterende netværk i det danske startup-økosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hvad Vi Tilbyder Dig&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Som vores Chief of Staff&amp;nbsp;vil du påbegynde en rejse, hvor du udvikler dig personligt og professionelt sammen med en gruppe drevne og ambitiøse kolleger. I denne rolle vil du styrke dine lederevner gennem projekter og coaching i det danske venturemiljø.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Et dynamisk og spændende arbejdsmiljø med ambitiøse og talentfulde kolleger&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;En kultur præget af kontinuerlig læring og udvikling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direkte indflydelse på CVX’s succes samt de porteføljevirksomheder, vi investerer i&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coaching og udviklingsmuligheder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;En kombination af fast løn og performance-baseret bonus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Startdato&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Så hurtigt som muligt.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As Chief of Staff to the CEO, you will work directly with Brian and the global Senior Management Team to drive strategic initiatives, accelerate execution, and ensure alignment across the organization. You will act as a force multiplier—bringing structure, clarity, and momentum to the company’s most important priorities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is not an administrative role. It is a strategic, facilitative leadership position requiring intellectual rigor, strong judgment, and the ability to move seamlessly between big-picture strategy and hands-on execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Partner with the CEO to shape, lead, and execute strategic initiatives and special projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Serve as a trusted advisor and sounding board to the CEO and senior leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Act as an “air traffic controller” for the leadership team—synthesizing information, connecting dots, and maintaining a holistic view of priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Facilitate executive road-mapping, business planning, and prioritization sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Coordinate and support key business management processes including budgeting, resourcing, and performance management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Drive cross-functional alignment and ensure follow-through on high-impact initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Operate with flexibility and speed in a dynamic, fast-paced global environment&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Why This Role Is Exciting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;multilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;A true leadership role with significant exposure to&amp;nbsp;operating&amp;nbsp;and scaling a global SaaS company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
