&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Pallet&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pallet is building AI Agents to transform logistics — a $12 trillion global industry. We’ve raised $50M from top investors including General Catalyst, Bessemer Venture Partners, and Bain Capital Ventures. In under two years, we’ve achieved 700% revenue growth and are just getting started.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission is to increase the efficiency of the global supply chain by automating the manual workflows that slow logistics teams down — from scheduling and appointment setting to data entry and load management. Our flagship platform provides end-to-end visibility, control, and optimization, while our newest product, CoPallet, introduces AI Agents that can understand and execute requests in real time, and integrate directly with customer systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As logistics providers look to generative AI to drive efficiency, many are turning to Pallet to lead the way. With deep industry expertise and cutting-edge AI capabilities, we’re positioned to build the next $10B company in logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us and work alongside leaders from Google, DoorDash, YC, and more to shape the future of logistics tech.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You could be a Chief of Staff anywhere, why us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join a well-funded, high-growth startup on the path to IPO ($50M raised, 700% revenue growth in 2 years, targeting a $6T market)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with our CEO &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/sushanth-raman/&quot;&gt;Sushanth Raman&lt;/a&gt; on the most critical aspects of the business and help drive key decisions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help transform a massive industry and scale us toward a $10 B+ business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the opportunity:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Chief of Staff to the Go-To-Market (GTM) leadership team, you’ll be a strategic partner to the CEO and GTM leaders, playing a critical role in scaling Pallet’s commercial impact. You’ll enable high-velocity decision-making, help us win at executive-level business development, and drive clarity and alignment across cross-functional initiatives. This is a high-visibility role with real ownership and a clear path into GTM leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you will make an impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;709&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;288&quot; data-end=&quot;434&quot;&gt;Partner directly with the Head of GTM and executive team to translate high-level strategy into clear priorities, operating plans, and timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;435&quot; data-end=&quot;564&quot;&gt;Own cross-functional GTM initiatives (sales, marketing, partnerships, customer success), ensuring alignment and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;565&quot; data-end=&quot;656&quot;&gt;Identify gaps, risks, and tradeoffs in GTM plans and proactively surface recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;565&quot; data-end=&quot;656&quot;&gt;Prepare leaders for executive, board, and customer-facing conversations by developing clear narratives, decks, and briefing materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Join key customer, partner, and internal leadership meetings; capture decisions, clarify next steps, and drive accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Coordinate across product, engineering, finance, and operations to ensure GTM needs are reflected in roadmaps and resourcing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Track commitments made by GTM leadership and ensure decisions turn into action.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Pressure-test assumptions, analyze tradeoffs, and support decision-making with data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;846&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;Draft and refine presentations, memos, and proposals for:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1533&quot; data-end=&quot;1622&quot;&gt;
