significant influence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;shaping how&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;the technology team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;, connecting cross-functional initiatives, and driving clarity on critical priorities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your impact will come from being the strategic partner and force multiplier that helps the technology leadership team move faster and execute more effectively.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
