&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Track and report&amp;nbsp;key performance metrics within the technology organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Help to coordinate communications, planning, and decision-making processes to support the&amp;nbsp;technology team&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;be a&amp;nbsp;liaison&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;other business&amp;nbsp;stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
