&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Experience:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;5-7+&amp;nbsp;years of experience&amp;nbsp;in managing projects that involve software engineers. Although you&amp;nbsp;don&#39;t&amp;nbsp;necessarily need to have a software engineering or infrastructure background, you need to be familiar with concepts in&amp;nbsp;the space.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Naturally Curious:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;You will need to rapidly absorb and contextualize information&amp;nbsp;in order to&amp;nbsp;quickly become conversant in new concepts and technology.&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;also need the humility to quickly and honestly acknowledge when&amp;nbsp;you&#39;re&amp;nbsp;out of your depth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Communication:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Exceptional written and verbal communicator, skilled at distilling complex material and concepts into straightforward language which everyone in our business can understand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Relationship Management:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Proven ability to build and manage relationships with technical&amp;nbsp;teams, executives, and external partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Strategic Thinking:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Strong bias for action, capable of setting priorities and executing in fast-paced environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Detail Orientation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;be interacting with and externally&amp;nbsp;representing&amp;nbsp;a technology function and organization which holds itself to&amp;nbsp;high standards. Building and&amp;nbsp;maintaining&amp;nbsp;credibility within this team will require precise attention to detail and an exacting standard of quality in your work product.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
