&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Cultural Leadership:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Passionate about fostering an inclusive, growth-oriented workplace.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Problem-Solving:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Structured thinker who balances short-term needs with long-term goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
