&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Responsibility:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;You must be self-motivated, capable of working from loose concepts at times, and getting work done in an extremely efficient fashion. You are someone who knows how to politely knock on doors and how&amp;nbsp;to kick&amp;nbsp;them in when&amp;nbsp;appropriate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
